<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id52f5bbeb-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6" identifier="/us/usc/t28/s3908"><num value="3908">§ 3908.</num><heading> Definitions</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">For purposes of applying this chapter, the terms “employing office” and “covered employee” have the meanings given those terms in <ref href="/us/usc/t3/s401">section 401 of title 3</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id52f5bbec-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/104/331/s3/c">Pub. L. 104–331, § 3(c)</ref>, <date date="1996-10-26">Oct. 26, 1996</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/110/4071">110 Stat. 4071</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
