<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="id52f5bbee-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="id52f5bbef-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section effective <date date="1997-10-01">Oct. 1, 1997</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/104/331/s3/d">section 3(d) of Pub. L. 104–331</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t28/s1296">section 1296 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
